畢業論文






















標題: 蜂巢式個人通訊服務系統中通道借用指派策略之研究Study on a Channel Borrowing Strategy in a Cellular-Based PCS System
作者: 黃柏鈞Po-Chiun Huang張仲儒Dr. Chung-Ju Chang電信工程研究所
關鍵字: 通道借用無需閉鎖,個人通訊服務系統;Channel Borrowing Without Locking, Personal Communication Service System
公開日期: 1994
摘要: 在蜂巢式行動通訊系統中，通道指派策略的優劣與否可由頻譜的使用效率
來決定，而頻譜的使用效率則可由發話阻塞機率及強迫通話中斷機率來衡
量。本篇論文將探討並評估在蜂巢式個人通訊服務系統中通道借用指派策
略的效能。首先，我們將通道借用指派策略設定為一種保護換手作用的方
法，同時提出一種近似的方法來分析此種系統的效能。並觀察出通道借用
指派策略對於換手作用的影響。我們也考慮通道借用策略同時使用在新來
呼叫及交手呼叫時的情形。而在通道借用指派策略中呼叫佇列及截止優先
權也在本篇論文的討論範圍中。我們的目的是分析通道借用指派策略的效
能，同時在一特定的系統效能評估標準下，找出新來呼叫的佇列長度、交
手呼叫的佇列長度及保護頻道數目的最佳組合。
In the cellular  mobile  communication  system, whether  a
channel assignment  strategy  is good or not is determined by
the utilization  of spectrum.  And the  utilization  of
spectrum can be measured by the blocking  probability  and the
forced termination probability. The thesis studies the
performance of a channel borrowing assignment strategy for a
cellular-based  PCS system.  First, we adopt the channel
borrowing strategy as a protection  scheme for handoff and
propose  an approximated  method  to  analyze  the  system
performance.  The effect of the channel borrowing strategy on
handoff  is investigated.  Ane  we also  consider  the channel
borrowing  strategy for both new calls and handoff calls;  the
call queueing and cutoff priority  used in the channel
borrowing strategy are discussed. Our objective is to  measure
the  performance  of  the  channel  borrowing strategy to
determine the optimal combination of the queue lengths  for
both new and handoff  calls and the number of guard  channels
given  a  specified   system  performance criterion.
URI: http://140.113.39.130/cdrfb3/record/nctu/#NT830436007http://hdl.handle.net/11536/59360
顯示於類別：畢業論文




















